topic: Movie Workflow Series ("The Batman movies explorative search")

goals.1: Investigate the works (aka derivative works) related to the Batman and individuate the movies. Return the movies along with the year of production and the director.
goals.2: Return the main Batman movie series produced in the last four decades and compare them in terms of length, number of actors involved and costs.
goals.3: Investigate what are the workers (writers, actors, etc.) who had a role in more Batman movies so far.
goals.4: Compare the ratings of the single movies and of the series. Indentify the movie with highest rating from the critics and the "best" series overall
goals.5: Return how many actors who are members of the cast of the "Dark Knight Trilogy" by Christopher Nolan have [Kavin Bacon number](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Six_Degrees_of_Kevin_Bacon#:~:text=Kevin%20Bacon%20himself%20has%20a,Bacon%20number%20is%20N%2B1.) equal to 2
